"1 tablespoon olive oil, divided","4 ounces fresh baby spinach","1  (8-oz.) prebaked thin pizza crust (such as Mama Mary's)","1/4 cup lower-sodium marinara sauce (such as Rao's)","4 ounces lower-sodium deli ham, diced","2 ounces shredded reduced-fat cheddar cheese (about 1/2 cup)","2 ounces fresh mozzarella cheese, torn","1/2 cup julienne-cut Fuji apple","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","1/4 teaspoon crushed red pepper"